parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle jerks or lunges forward
the transmission makes a loud whining or grinding noise
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the PTCM can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle jerks or lunges forward
the transmission makes a loud whining or grinding noise
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the shifter can cause the vehicle to become stuck in park or unable to shift into gear, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The shifter is stuck in park
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear
the shifter makes a loud grinding or clunking noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine mounts can cause the vehicle to vibrate excessively, leading to loss of control or accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle vibrates excessively
the engine makes a loud noise
the engine lifts off the motor mounts.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine cradle and mounts can cause the vehicle to involuntarily swerve into other lanes of traffic, leading to accidents and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle swerves or pulls to one side
the engine cradle or mounts are damaged or broken
the vehicle's steering becomes difficult to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the vehicle to become difficult to steer, leading to accidents and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The power steering fails or becomes difficult to use
the steering wheel becomes hard to turn
the vehicle's steering becomes unresponsive.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling of the vehicle and loss of power can cause the vehicle to become difficult to control, leading to accidents and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the engine dies
the power steering and brakes fail
the vehicle becomes difficult to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the fuel gauge malfunctions
the fuel system fails to function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling and Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden stalling of the engine can cause loss of power steering and braking, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls while driving
often without warning
and may lose power steering and braking. The engine may also shake or make a loud noise before stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of motor mounts can cause the engine to lift or jump, leading to damage to other components and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The engine shakes or lifts while driving
making a loud noise or causing the vehicle to vibrate. The motor mounts may also break or fracture
leading to further damage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and transmission can cause the vehicle to jerk or stall, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the vehicle jerks or stalls while shifting gears
or the transmission makes a loud noise or slips while driving.

symptoms: Intermittent failures of headlights
windshield wipers
and dashboard instruments
loss of power
stalling
and inability to shift gears.

stalling
